item.title: CVE-2023-2263|2024-08-02T06:19:14.499Z -- rockwell%20automation -- kinetix%205700%20dc%20bus%20power%20supply%20series%20a
item.description: The Rockwell Automation Kinetix 5700 DC Bus Power Supply Series A is vulnerable to CIP fuzzing. The new ENIP connections cannot be established if impacted by this vulnerability, which prohibits operational capabilities of the device resulting in a denial-of-service attack.
